data.description: This beautiful 4 bedroom home in Dallastown is convenient to York, 83 and not far from Maryland.  A dream come true for commuters!  Hardwood flooring, open hardwood stairs, gorgeous kitchen with newer white cabinets, a huge kitchen island that offers more seating and granite throughout! Fully Finished basement has  a lovely wood burning fireplace,  2nd bathroom with forth bedroom and a garage.  Newly renovated home with an awesome inground pool and vinyl fenced in yard  privacy.  This one won't last long!  Call today to schedule your private showing. Save tons of $$ Seller has a low VA assumable loan!
